Title: Waje Remakes ''Raise The Roof'' By Jazzman Olofin ft Adewale Ayuba
Description: On this episode of Accelerate TV’s Audio Candy, soulful singer, Waje, entertains us with a special rendition of her single 'In The Air'. On the other half of the show she performs the cover of the classic Jazzman Olofin’s song 'Raise The Roof'. Enjoy!
